          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Police in Germany believe a man who appeared to be sleeping the driver’s seat of his Tesla had Autopilot engaged while traveling down the Autobahn. That’s right, the roadway where in many areas there’s no speed limit doesn’t seem like the kind of place one would just let a computer do the driving, but we suppose when you live around it the thrill might wear off. Or maybe it was the drugs.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
